data.description: Situated on 1+ acres this 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home offers 1,816 square feet of comfortable living space in a serene Pleasant Valley neighborhood. Upon entering, you'll notice the new flooring that leads you through the main areas of the home. The living room provides a cozy spot for family gatherings or simply relaxing at the end of the day. The kitchen has been thoughtfully updated to include stainless steel appliances and a tasteful subway tile backsplash. Whether preparing daily meals or hosting friends, this kitchen offers functionality and style. Both full bathrooms have been nicely updated, while the additional half bath adds an extra touch of convenience. The three bedrooms provide ample space for guests, with the primary bedroom featuring its own full bathroom. Outside, the sizable 1.18-acre yard invites possibilities for gardening, play, or simply enjoying the outdoors. This is a home where practical updates and comfortable living come together. Conveniently located close to the Taconic State Parkway and Route 44, enjoy all the Hudson Valley has to offer at your doorstep. Don't miss the opportunity to view this property. Schedule your tour today!
